Name: Average resolution time difference between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time spent in 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average time leading up to 'Completed + In Call' from the start of a case
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time difference between 'Completed + In Call' completion and 'Completed + Closed' initiation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases where it directly follows 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' across cases with 'Medium' impact
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time taken to reach 'Completed + In Call' from 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Maximum duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases involving 'PROD582' product
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Difference in average duration between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases originating from 'France'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Completed + In Call' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases with 'High' impact
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002583FC292D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS filtered by the function ma == 'High' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Shortest time to 'Completed + In Call' from case start in 'USA' cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases that also include 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Duration of 'Completed + In Call' in the variant with the highest performance score
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with more than two activities following 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
